 Scheme for Disabled Children of Labourers EligibilityUnder the \u0905\u0915\u094d\u0937\u092e \u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u094b \u0935\u093f\u0924\u094d\u0924\u0940\u092f \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e of Haryana Labour Welfare Board, labour dept. provide Rs. 2,000 per month to disabled children of registered labourers who have 50% or more physical / mental disability. The eligibility criteria to avail assistance under Haryana Labour Assistance Scheme for Disabled Children of Labourers are as follows:-Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093eMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e0Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940YesHaryana Labour Department Assistance Scheme for Disabled Children of Labourers ConditionsPeople can follow the below mentioned conditions to avail financial aid under Labour Welfare Board Aksham Baccho Ko Vittiya Sahayata Yojana in Haryana:-All the registered labourers must have minimum 1 years of membership / subscription.In the identity certificate of the registered labourers, registration fees and subscription amount needs to be mentioned.The children of registered labourers must be declared 50% or more physically / mentally disabled by any medical authority.Along with the completed application form, Disability Certificate issued by medical authority must be attached.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}